obj_root_law_sections_9_content:
  string
  line `Nothing in section 4 or section 5 shall apply to money`
  line `belonging to any estate for the purpose of the administration of which the Regimental Debts Act, 1893`
  line `(56 & 57 Viet., c.5), applies.`
